quran[58]{c,v,t}:
  75,1,“Ndikulumbilira tsiku lachimaliziro
  75,2,“Ndikulumbiliranso mzimu wodzidzudzula (pa cholakwa chimene wachita. Ndithu mudzaukitsidwa; mafupa anu omwazikana atasonkhanitsidwa)
  75,3,“Kodi munthu akuganiza kuti Ife (Amene tidamlenga kuchokera popanda chilichonse) sitidzatha kusonkhanitsa mafupa ake (ofumbwa)
  75,4,"“Iyayi, Ife tikhoza (kutisonkhanitsa) ndi kutilongosola bwino timizere takunsonga kwa zala zake. (Mafupa ake ndiye osanena)"
  75,5,“Koma munthu akufuna kuti apitirize kuchimwa (mmasiku akudza) mtsogolo mwake
  75,6,"“Akufunsa (mwa chipongwe): “Kodi lidzakhala liti tsiku la chimaliziro?”"
  75,7,“Pamene maso adzangoti tong’oo (ndi mantha)
  75,8,“Ndi kuchoka kuwala kwa mwezi
  75,9,“Ndipo dzuwa ndi mwezi ndikusonkhanitsidwa
  75,10,"“Munthu adzanena tsiku limenelo: “Nkuti kothawira (chilangochi?)”"
  75,11,"“(Adzauzidwa): “Iyayi, (iwe munthu) palibe pothawira (pako)!”"
  75,12,“Tsiku limenelo kobwerera (anthu) ndi kwa Mbuye wako basi
  75,13,“Tsiku limenelo munthu adzauzidwa zochita zake zimene adazitsogoza ndi zimene adazichedwetsa
  75,14,“Koma munthu adzadzichitira umboni yekha pa mzimu wake
  75,15,“Ngakhale atapereka madandaulo ake (otani kuti apulumuke nawo sadzapulumuka)
  75,16,“Usaigwedezere (Qur’an) lirime lako (pamene ikuvumbulutsidwa) kuti uifulumilire (kuiwerenga ndi kuisunga mu mtima)
  75,17,“Ndithu ndiudindo wathu kuisonkhanitsa (mu mtima mwako) ndi kukhazikitsa kawerengedwe kake (palirime lako)
  75,18,“Choncho pamene tikukuwerengera iwe tsatira kuwerenga kwakeko (uku uli chete)
  75,19,"“Kenako, ndithu ndiudindo Wathu kulongosola (zimene siukumvetsa)"
  75,20,“Iyayi koma mukukonda moyo wa pa dziko
  75,21,“Ndipo mukusiya moyo wa tsiku lachimaliziro
  75,22,“Nkhope zina tsiku limenelo zidzakhala zowala
  75,23,“Zili kumuyang’ana Mbuye wawo
  75,24,“Ndipo nkhope zina tsiku limenelo zidzakhala zoziya (zokhwinyata)
  75,25,“Zikuyembekezeka kuti zilandira tsoka lodula msana
  75,26,"“Sichoncho! Pamene mzimu udzafika pa nthitimtima, (pomwe pakumana mafupa am’mapewa)"
  75,27,“Ndipo ndikunenedwa ndani angamchiritse
  75,28,"“Ndipo (iye mwini wake), nkutsimikiza kuti ndithu uku ndikusiyana (ndi dziko lapansi)"
  75,29,“Ndipo miyendo idzasanjikizana; (iyi ndi nthawi yochoka mzimu)
  75,30,“Tsiku limenelo koperekedwa (anthu onse) nkwa Mbuye wako
  75,31,“Ndipo sadakhulupirire komanso sadapemphere Swala (zisanu)
  75,32,“Koma (m’malo mwake) adatsutsa ndi kunyoza
  75,33,“Kenaka adapita kubanja lake (uku akuyenda) monyada
  75,34,“Kuonongeka nkwako (iwe wotsutsa)! Kuonongeka zedi
  75,35,“Ndiponso kuonongeka nkwako! kuonongeka zedi
  75,36,“Kodi munthu akuganiza kuti angosiidwa chabe? (Sadzaweruzidwa)
  75,37,“Kodi sadali dontho la umuna umene udafwamphukira (m’chiberekero)
  75,38,"“Kenako adakhala nthinthi (ntchintchi) ya magazi, ndipo adamlenga ndi kumlinganiza (monga munthu)"
  75,39,"“Ndipo adalenga kuchokera mmenemo mitundu iwiri: mwamuna ndi mkazi"
  75,40,“Kodi (Iye amene adayambitsa chilengedwe choyambachi) sangathe kuwapatsa moyo akufa
  76,1,“Ndithu munthu idampita nthawi yaitali kwambiri (asanauziridwe mzimu) pomwe sadali chinthu chotchulidwa
  76,2,“Ndithu Ife tamlenga munthu kuchokera ku mbewu ya munthu yosakanikirana (ya mkazi ndi ya mwamuna) kuti timuyese mayeso (ndi malamulo Athu); choncho tidampanga kukhala wakumva ndi wopenya; (amve mawu a Allah ndi kuti aone zisonyezo Zake)
  76,3,"“Ndithu Ife tidamlongosolera njira yoongoka: kukhala wokhulupirira kapena wotsutsa (Zonse zili kwa iye)"
  76,4,“Ndithu Ife okana tawakonzera unyolo (wam’miyendo yawo) ndi magoli (am’manja ndi m’makosi awo) ndi Moto waukali woyaka
  76,5,"“Ndithu ochita zabwino adzamwa vinyo, chosakanizira chake chidzakhala (madzi a) kaafura"
  76,6,“(Kaafura ameneyo) ndikasupe amene adzikamwapo akapolo a Allah ndi kumtulutsa (paliponse pamene afuna) kumtulutsa mofewa
  76,7,"“(Amene) akukwaniritsa zimene adalonjeza (okha kwa Allah), ndiponso akuopa tsiku (lalikulu) limene zoipa zake zidzakhala zofalikira ponseponse"
  76,8,"“Ndipo amadyetsa chakudya masikini, amasiye ndi ogwidwa pa nkhondo, pomwe iwo akuchifunanso"
  76,9,"“Amanena (chamumtima akamapereka chakudyacho): “Tikukudyetsani chifukwa chofuna chikondi cha Allah basi; sitikufuna kwa inu malipiro kapena kuthokoza"
  76,10,“Ndithu ife tikuopa kwa Mbuye wathu tsiku lokhwinyata nkhope ndi mavuto akulu.”
  76,11,“Ndipo Allah adzawateteza mu mavuto a tsiku limenelo ndiponso adzawapatsa mtendere ndi chisangalalo
  76,12,“Ndipo adzawalipira chifukwa cha kupirira kwawo Munda wamtendere ndi nsalu zaveleveti
  76,13,“Atatsamira m’menemo pa makama (amtengo wapatali); sadzamva m’menemo kutentha kwa dzuwa kapena kuzizira
  76,14,“Mithunzi yake ikawayandikira iwo ndipo mikoko yazipatso idzatewa pafupi (moti munthu atha kuthyola ali chigonere)
  76,15,“Ndipo adzakhala akuzunguliridwa (ndi otumikira) uku atatenga zomwera za siliva ndi matambula onyezimira ndiponso olangala
  76,16,"“Zolangala zopangidwa ku siliva, atalinga bwino zakumwazo (malinga ndi kufuna kwawo)"
  76,17,"“Ndipo (anthu abwino) akamwetsedwa kumeneko vinyo, chosakanizira chake chikafanana ndi Zanjabila (chikasu)"
  76,18,“M’menemo muli kasupe wotchedwa Salisabila